Team Le Grand

Pathway explored : REACTOME SEMAPHORIN INTERACTIONS

This pathway contain 64 genes.

In these 64 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.

Inside these differents genes, there are (cf table below) number of genes DE significant with a major participation in the enrichment (leadingEdge cal by fgsea filter by padj<0.05).
